original_title: Down The Coast - A Cab-Ride Spectacular Crewe - Holyhead
overview: This film shows a cab ride from Crewe to Holyhead on-board 37418 ‘East Lancashire Railway’ for a trip down the coast from Crewe to Holyhead in the days of locomotive haulage.
title: Down The Coast - A Cab-Ride Spectacular Crewe - Holyhead
